	<div class="story">
		<p class="endText">Most of what follows was written a few years ago [2020: at least fifteen] but you can get up-to-date information on the latest in less-environmentally-damaging cars at <a class="external" target="_blank" href="http://www.autobloggreen.com/">AutoBlogGreen</a>.</p>
