	<h2>Smart car</h2>
	<div class="story">
		<p class="endText">I was pleased to see lots of these during our 2002 trip to France and Holland because they initially didn't sell well.  Originally started by the watch company Swatch with Mercedes-Benz having a financial interest, MB finally took over and brought its full engineering expertise to bear before it was brought to market. It is exactly 2500mm long which must make it a joy to park but I wish it were prettier. [Aug07 update: the new model is 2695mm long and it is coming to the US in 2008, though sadly, not the diesel version.]</p>
